          <button class="sp-faqx-tab" data-cat="process" aria-selected="false"><span class="sp-faqx-tab-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Process</button>
        </nav>
        <div class="sp-faqx-panels" id="faq-panels">
          <div class="sp-faqx-panel active" data-cat="problems" role="list">
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">Do you calculate the firebox-to-flue ratios in-house?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">Yes. While we follow the architect's vision, our foremen verify all thermodynamic ratios (Rumford principles) to ensure the open hearth will actually draft smoke correctly before we begin laying block.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">Are your custom chimneys fully up to local fire codes?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">Absolutely. We rigidly adhere to all local municipal codes regarding combustible clearances, hearth extensions, and firebox depths to guarantee your custom build passes inspection instantly.</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-faqx-panel" data-cat="cost" role="list">
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">Can you match the exterior chimney veneer to the rest of the home?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">Yes, this is standard practice. We utilize the identical brick or natural stone used on the home's primary facade, maintaining exact mortar coloration for a completely unified luxury aesthetic.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">What do you use for the chimney crown?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">We do not use cheap mortar washes. We pour thick, custom concrete crowns featuring integrated overhangs and drip edges. This permanent solution prevents water from running down the exterior masonry.</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-faqx-panel" data-cat="repair" role="list">
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">How long does a full custom chimney stack take to build?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">Depending on the height and complexity of the veneer, a full stack typically requires 1 to 2 weeks. We coordinate the specific timeline with the framing and roofing crews to ensure the house is sealed rapidly.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">When do we schedule the masonry phase for the hearth?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">We typically construct the firebox and interior stack concurrent with framing, and return for the exterior veneer when the rest of the exterior cladding is scheduled, though we adapt to your GC's preferences.</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-faqx-panel" data-cat="process" role="list">
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">Will you use subcontractors to expedite the chimney build?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">Never. Building a functional fireplace is highly specialized. We rely 100% on our own vetted, long-term AMS employees to ensure the safety and functionality of the hearth.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-faqx-item" role="listitem">
              <button class="sp-faqx-q" aria-expanded="false">Do you also do chimney repairs or rebuilds?</button>
              <div class="sp-faqx-a" aria-hidden="true"><div class="sp-faqx-a-inner">Yes. While we focus heavily on new luxury construction, we also offer complete structural chimney rebuilds and historic restorations for existing high-end properties. See our Chimney Repair page for details.</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
